#. type: Plain text
#: ../../../../../doc/misc/gnus-faq.texi:170
msgid ""
"Gnus is released independent from releases of Emacs.  Therefore, the version "
"bundled with Emacs might not be up to date (e.g., Gnus 5.9 bundled with "
"Emacs 21 is outdated).  You can get the latest released version of Gnus from "
"@uref{https://www.gnus.org/dist/gnus.tar.gz} or from "
"@uref{https://ftp.gnus.org/pub/gnus/gnus.tar.gz}."
